    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "In the st Thomas college of arts and science , there is no unwanted activities are happened in our college campus because the students are supervising by the CCTV camera and the securities",
          "name": "Marimuthu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "In our college the drugs are prohibited in college campus,if any students used any types drugs in our college they are strictly punished by our college management",
          "name": "Marimuthu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "In the St Thomas College of arts and science, there is no ragging activities among the students because our college very focus on the discipline",
          "name": "Vigneshwar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "In the St Thomas College of arts and science the campus should be clean and clear and there is a big and  wonderful auditorium",
          "name": "Vigneshwar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "In the St Thomas College of arts and science shift 2 coaching is better than shift 1 because the faculty members are very friendly with students",
          "name": "Vigneshwar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college management concern about the women safety the college have the women safety club if the students faced any harassment they can able to companit in that office and the staffs take a seviour punishment on the student or staff thar harrased",
          "name": "Sundareshwaran",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The st thomas college of arts and science have the  clean campus they provide drinking water in most of the places its help maintain hydrate at summer times and the students vehicles are parked in the seperate place and the vehicles are protected",
          "name": "Sundareshwaran",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "In st thomas college of arts  science  the staffs are very friendly we can able to clarify our doubts thar related to subjects at anytime they never hesitate to teach and the teachers help to score more marks in our university exams",
          "name": "Sundareshwaran",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "They provide better teaching strategies to make students understand the concepts better.",
          "name": "KANISHKAR",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the environment where everyone feels confortable it is not only thing i liked it is also said by my batchmates.",
          "name": "KANISHKAR",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Comparatively very small campus and infrastructure facilities in St Thomas college they have to improve this problem",
          "name": "Nivedha S",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "in our college campus the basket ball ground and foot ball ground are very small and there is limited resources, and students need permission to play on the ground",
          "name": "Marimuthu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our college management treating students like school students because they arranged the parents meeting in every semester before the exam starts",
          "name": "Marimuthu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "In the st Thomas college of arts and science the college management is very strict because if they students take leave they sent the message to the parents",
          "name": "Marimuthu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "In our college we cannot able to roam freely in the college campus because there is so many rules and regulations",
          "name": "Vigneshwar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "In our college there is very small play gound for students and students are struggling to play the cricket in our college campus",
