        },
        {
          "text": "Comparatively st Thomas College campus is  very small and low infrastructure facilities",
          "name": "Vigneshwar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "And the last thing i hate in st Thomas college of arts and science is test the teacher only concerned about study the doesn't care about students mentality they only aimed to complete the chapters they doesn't care about students",
